                        <div class="text2 space">
                            <p>Photoshop <br> Illustrator <br> Adobe XD <br> Premier Pro <br> Lightroom</p>
                        </div>
    
                        <div class="text3 space">
                            <p>After Effects <br> Illustrator <br> InDesign <br> Premier Pro <br> GitHub</p>
